channel.title: My sister
channel.description:
So my mom asked me to head to the store and buy christmas presents and decorations for my 7 year old sister's christmas celebrations at school. I've spent 40 minutes of my life (40 minutes which I had planned to spend sleeping before I head out to training) picking decorations, untangling balloons that were tangled as hell, watching her complain about the store, change her decisions three times at least, then finally settling on a 6 face puzzle that completely sucks balls.
We then proceeded to move out of the store when she tells me "Well it took you long enough!". So now you can see how hairy the nuts my life sucks are.
